app: The COVID Alert DE smartphone app will help limit the spread of the virus in our community by letting you know if you’ve been close to someone who later tests positive.
contact_tracing: For contact tracing, public health staff work with an individual who has tested positive for COVID-19 to help them identify everyone with whom they have had close contact during the timeframe while they may have been infectious.
self_reporting: If the positive COVID-19 test is from a test that is not administered from Student Health Services, the student is encouraged to report this information to Student Health Services.
